.row.justify-content-center.mt-4
  .col-md-8
    %h1.fw-bold About Bookify
    %p.lead.text-muted
      An open-source freelancer payment marketplace built on the
      %a{href: "https://payoutpartner.com", target: "_blank"} Payout Partner
      API v2.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold What is Bookify?
        %p
          Bookify is a complete, working two-sided marketplace that demonstrates how to
          onboard freelancers, create bookings, process payouts, and bundle invoices using
          POP's REST API.
        %p.mb-0
          It's built for operators and developers who want to build their own
          freelancer payment platform. Clone it, customize it, or just read the code.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold How it works
        .row.g-3.mt-2
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 1
              %div
                %strong Booker invites a freelancer
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Enter their email — they receive a link to accept.
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 2
              %div
                %strong Freelancer verifies identity
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Through POP's secure BankID/ID verification flow.
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 3
              %div
                %strong Booker logs work and pays
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Create bookings with hours and rate, then trigger payouts.
          .col-md-6
            .d-flex.align-items-start
              %span.badge.rounded-pill.bg-primary.me-3.mt-1 4
              %div
                %strong POP handles the rest
                %p.text-muted.small.mb-0 Invoicing, tax reporting, and bank transfer.

    .card.border-0.shadow-sm.my-4
      .card-body.p-4
        %h4.fw-bold Links
        %ul.list-unstyled.mb-0
          %li.mb-2
            %i.bi.bi-github.me-2
            %a{href: "https://github.com/payoutpartner/bookify-app", target: "_blank"} Source code on GitHub
          %li.mb-2
            %i.bi.bi-globe.me-2
            %a{href: "https://payoutpartner.com", target: "_blank"} Payout Partner
          %li
            %i.bi.bi-file-code.me-2
            %a{href: "https://sandbox.core.payoutpartner.com/api-docs", target: "_blank"} POP API documentation
